info:
KEY ACCOUNTABILITIES OF ROLE

PLAY THE ROLE OF COMPLIANCE INTERN TO SUPPORT THE COMPLIANCE RELATED WORK, INCLUDING:
•	ASSIST THE LINE MANAGER TO REVIEW THE SUPPORTING DOCUMENTS TO ENSURE BUSINESS ACTIVITIES WITH HCPS/GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS ARE PLANNED IN CONSISTENCE WITH APPLICABLE POLICIES AND PROCEDURES;
•	ASSIST TO CHECK THE COMPLETENESS OF DOCUMENTS FOR PROJECT APPLICATION;
•	PERFORM RESEARCH ON EXTERNAL POLICIES AND PROCEDURES;
•	RECORD MEETING MINUTES OF INTERVIEW WITH 3RD PARTY;
•	OTHER TASKS AS NEEDED.


QUALIFICATIONS, KNOWLEDGE & SKILLS REQUIRED
•	BACHELOR AND ABOVE IN THE MAJOR OF ACCOUNTING, AUDIT, LEGAL, OR FINANCE MANAGEMENT RELATED;
•	GOOD COMMUNICATION AND LOGICAL THINKING SKILLS;
•	ABILITY TO WORK UNDER PRESSURE AND MEET THE DEADLINE;
•	DATA ANALYSIS SKILL IS A PLUS.

工作内容：

1.负责公司产品图片后期处理，拍摄，精修，排版等;

2. 根据产品特点，准确把握产品卖点，充分展示产品形象和特点;

3. 负责产品页面，店铺装修大促海报等;

4. 能通过图片设计和优化的渲染，挖掘产品亮点，卖点，提升产品销量和整体品质;

备注：此岗位可线上实习，实习优秀可转正。

工作职责
1、协助项目公开信息初步筛查、整理;
2、协助项资产池每日盯市预警;
3、协助项目管理和贷后材料的收集与整理:
4、协助项目尽职调查、参与调研会议、协助整理笔录等,
5、部门领导安排的其他任务。

任职资格
1、2025年及以后毕业;硕士及以上学位在读，金融、法律相关专业优先;
2、具备良好的沟通及理解能力，有一定的服务精神，工作积极主动;
3具有较强的学习能力、研究能力、逻辑思维能力、言语和书面表达能力、人际沟通能力，富有责任心;
4、能够承受一定的工作压力，具备团队合作精神和分享意识;能够协助团队进行简单公司及行业研究分析，资源整理等相关工作;
5、具备券商资产管理业务相关知识，了解银行、信托、基金等机构的相关业务
有券商资产管理、基金行业实习经验者优先;
6、能保证每周出勤3天及以上，实习期不少于3个月.

Job Description:
1. Assist Underwriter to set up Printing document of Marine Product;
2. Translation of Brouchure and marketing materials;
3. Documentation;
4. Assist Underwriter to develop IT System requirement of Mmarine Products;
5. Process data in related system
6. Draft Quotation / Policy
7. Wording polish, etc.
Requirements:
- Expected attendance days per week: 3-5 days
- Preferred major in Law / Insurance / Finance (junior undergraduates or first-year or second-year graduates)
- Fluent in English, with team spirit and strong sense of responsibility
